{"tid":499749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蠔涌片廠爆炸品案 三被告分別被判監26至46個月","createTime":"2017-12-15T07:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T13:20:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef8734f8aed814d0494a10175ff0213c2943de3","tid":499749,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171215/57584680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57584680&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=42c57b73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57584680&h=e975c273\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171215/57584680</a><br />\n<br />\n警方前年6月拘捕5名男子，指他們涉嫌於西貢蠔涌亞視舊片廠串謀製造煙霧彈，事後在現場及其中兩人的家中撿獲爆炸品。5人早前否認控罪，於高等法院受審，最終其中3名被告陳耀成、鄭偉成及彭艾烈罪名成立，今依次被判監2年2個月、2年10個月及3年10個月。<br />\n<br />\n5名被告陳耀成（36歲）、鄭偉成（31歲）、彭艾烈（24歲）、胡啟賦（22歲）及文廷洛（24歲）被控於前年5月28日至6月14日期間，串謀在西貢蠔涌亞視舊片廠製造爆炸品罪。另外，陳、鄭各被控一項管有爆炸品罪，而彭則涉兩項管有爆炸品罪。最終鄭、彭被裁定串謀製造爆炸品及管有爆炸品罪成，而陳亦被裁定管有爆炸品罪成。胡及文則罪脫。根據《刑事罪行條例》，製造或管有爆炸品一經定罪，最高可判處14年監禁。"},{"pid":"bb6c86f2e2c3647c234117889f22d2b1dab1c888","tid":499749,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"施恒因不誠實取用電腦等罪，昨被判監<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">廿七</span></span>個月<br />\n<br />\n公平咩"},{"pid":"ae01925be477717774e0c99df6ef52300e34b976","tid":499749,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T07:09:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"551f5b6e770aea9231ab2418a4a49254c198e9b8","tid":499749,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6425b7be77fd9ee08c38dff8a38bc453038e1c","tid":499749,"uid":